      "description": "Offering a concours-level E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six. This example is mechanically flawless, boasting a recently overhauled VANOS system and a proactively reinforced rear subframe to ensure structural integrity. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission offers precise shift gates, delivering power through a perfectly calibrated M-variable differential. The suspension retains its factory-correct geometry with refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers for optimal corner-exit stability. Finished in Carbon Black over Cinnamon Nappa leather, the exterior exhibits zero clear coat failure or orange peel, while the engine bay is free of any fluid weepage or vacuum leaks. A turn-key specimen for the serious collector seeking peak longitudinal and lateral performance.",
